original_title: VxS vs No Peace Underground Already Dead
overview: Start the new year off strong and watch VxS and No Peace Underground spotlight and showcase Ultraviolence with "Already Dead" streaming live on FITE on January 7th!  The main event features the NPU Heavyweight Championship where JTG takes on Parrow for the title.  Also featuring Alex Zayne, John Wayne Murdoch, AJ Gray, Masha Slamovich, Vincent, Jordan Oliver, Atticus Cogar and more
title: VxS vs No Peace Underground Already Dead
